{"tid":2454083,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"AC米蘭教練向曼聯方面道歉 當時這番粗口被曝光","createTime":"2021-03-20T03:13:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T04:17:54.000Z","uid":34571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3a195d981a65c125d9be138b3e2eb4ea7fede3eb","tid":2454083,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T03:13:09.000Z","msg":"AC米蘭教練皮奧利向曼聯方面道歉。<br />\n<br />\n  據《太陽報》披露，在歐霸盃交鋒結束後，曼聯教練組的麥肯納和皮奧利有言語衝突，麥肯納對皮奧利嘲諷說「好球隊」，而皮奧利卻回應說：「好球隊個X，你什麼都不是就是個Axxxxxx，你姐姐有一支好球隊（指情人數量多）。」<br />\n<br />\n  如今，皮奧利為此道歉：「我對我的反應感到抱歉，這本不該發生，我祝賀了蘇斯克查，只是對他的助手感到氣憤。」"},{"pid":"6c77813cc2f24aff52e18a038e846a6445b6da3b","tid":2454083,"uid":25900,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T03:53:20.000Z","msg":"讚你隊波好又嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4911339382d8b8472522cf65348f73e7794a13fb","tid":2454083,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T04:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e6628c9a25517b7f94c3e02ee9e084213acb68","tid":2454083,"uid":34689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T04:17:54.000Z","msg":"支持樓主"}]}